#Text=Do you notice a difference between playing in front of British and American audiences ?
#Text=The U.S. audiences are much more full of expression and noises and jubilation .
#Text=They are like , " Welcome to New York , Baby ! "
#Text=" You 're Awesome ! " and stuff like that .
#Text=Whereas in England they tend to be a lot more reserved .
#Text=Well , the English are , but it is such a diverse culture you will get the Spanish and Italian gay guys at the front who are going crazy .
#Text=I definitely think in America they are much more open and there is more excitement , which is really cool .
#Text=How many instruments do you play and , please , include the glockenspiel in that number .
#Text=[ Laughs ]
#Text=I think the number is limitless , hopefully .
#Text=I try my hand at anything I can contribute ; I only just picked up the bass , really —
#Text=-- I have a great photo of you playing the bass .
#Text=I do n't think I 'm very good ...
#Text=You look cool with it !
#Text=[ Laughs ]
#Text=Fine .
#Text=The glockenspiel ... piano , mainly , and also the harp .
#Text=Guitar , I like playing percussion and drumming .
#Text=I usually speak with all my drummers so that I write my songs with them in mind , and we 'll have bass sounds , choir sounds , and then you can multi-task with all these orchestral sounds .
#Text=Through the magic medium of technology I can play all kinds of sounds , double bass and stuff .
#Text=Do you design your own clothes ?
#Text=All four of us girls love vintage shopping and charity shops .
#Text=We do n't have a stylist who tells us what to wear , it 's all very much our own natural styles coming through .
#Text=And for me , personally , I like to wear jewelery .
#Text=On the night of the New York show that top I was wearing was made especially for me as a gift by these New York designers called Pepper + Pistol .
#Text=And there 's also my boyfriend , who is an amazing musician —
#Text=— that 's Will Lemon from Moon and Moon , right ?
#Text=There is such good buzz about them here in New York .
#Text=Yes !
#Text=They have an album coming out in February and it will fucking blow your mind !
#Text=I think you would love it , it 's an incredible masterpiece .
#Text=It 's really exciting , I 'm hoping we can do a crazy double unfolding caravan show , the Bat for Lashes album and the new Moon and Moon album :
#Text=that would be really theatrical and amazing !
#Text=Will prints a lot of my T-shirts because he does amazing tapestries and silkscreen printing on clothes .
#Text=When we play there 's a velvety kind of tapestry on the keyboard table that he made .
#Text=So I wear a lot of his things , thrift store stuff , old bits of jewelry and antique pieces .
